      <title>Redbox 所有者因涉嫌管理不善将被清算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/redbox-owner-to-be-liquidated-following-alleged-mismanagement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，法官裁定，Redbox Entertainment Inc. 破产所有者将被清算，此前该公司和债权人的律师指控其前首席执行官管理不善，未能向员工支付工资或提供医疗福利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/redbox-owner-to-be-liquidated-following-alleged-mismanagement</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 00:21:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
